All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<O>, Collection<O>, Set<O>
public class ObjectStoreAsSet<O>
extends AbstractSet<O>

Adapts an ObjectStore to behave like a Set, using an existing connection to the persistence when methods belonging to the Set interface are called.
